
To release new version:

- change aChromaseqIntro information
- update notices.xml and install.xml
- turn on Debug mode in Mesquite, restart, and then zip the chromaseq directory using File>Zip Folder for Installer
- move chromaseq.zip to http://mesquiteproject.org/packages/chromaseq/

- move latest notices.xml and install.xml to http://mesquiteproject.org/packages/chromaseq/
- upload new version of manual to /packages/chromaseq/
- send email to chromaseq list

=============


Chromaseq version 1.0 requires Mesquite 2.75 plus the following:

To release:
	UndoInstructions
	MesquiteModule
